terization. We also\nderive improved lower bounds for several variants of the sum-product problem in\nadditive combinatorics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Jan 2014 07:09:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 19 Mar 2014 19:44:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-03-20"}
