. The positive correlations between the ratio of line\nwidth to energy and the corresponding depth for both two lines support a\ncylindrical column accretion geometry in Vela X-1.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Jan 2014 07:25:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
